@startuml cross-vertical-access-sequence
actor "Education Auditor" as EA
participant "Security System" as SS
participant "Health Service" as HS
participant "Consent System" as CS
participant "Audit System" as AS

EA -> SS : Request CROSS-VERTICAL Access (Target=HealthData)
SS -> AS : Log CROSS-VERTICAL Request

SS -> CS : Check Education-to-Health Shared Consent for Subject
CS --> SS : Valid (Intersection Rule applied)

SS -> HS : Fetch Data (Masked for Auditor)
HS --> SS : Data Stream
SS -> AS : Log Cross-Vertical DATA_CONSUMED
SS --> EA : Return Masked Response

@enduml
